results.title: Daemon X Machina: Titanic Scion - Official Fusion Trailer
creator: IGN Middle East
results.description: Learn about the Fusion System gameplay mechanic in this new Daemon X Machina: Titanic Scion trailer for the upcoming dark sci-fi action game. The Fusion system allows players to fuse Immortal factors, obtained from defeated enemies, into their bodies to acquire powerful abilities useful in combat. Daemon X Machina: Titanic Scion will be available on Nintendo Switch 2, PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and Windows PC via Steam on September 5, 2025.

results.title: EU Sanctions Hit Petroleum Sales of Russia-Linked Indian Refiner
creator: Charles Kennedy
results.description: While many analysts said that the latest EU sanctions against Russia would be moot without U.S. support, one Indian refiner partly owned by Russia’s oil giant Rosneft has been hit hard by the EU measures against Russian oil customers. India-based Nayara Energy, which owns the country’s third-largest refinery with a capacity of 400,000 barrels per day (bpd) and which is 49% owned by Rosneft, has troubles selling the fuels it has produced. results.title: Hell is Us - Official 'Diving into the Dungeons' Overview Trailer
creator: IGN Middle East
results.description: Watch the 'Diving into the Dungeons' Overview Trailer for Hell is Us, a third-person action-adventure game developed by Rogue Factor. While the heart of Hell is Us is composed of player intrigue with no quest markers or way points, the world is peppered with intentionally crafted dungeons that combine environmental puzzles and impactful combat encounters to create meaningful moments of exploration and tension. Get the full rundown on how Dungeons will challenge players in Hell is Us, launching on September 4 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC.
